data.description: Welcome home to 508 Berkshire Terrace! This lovely home on a corner lot has refinished floors downstairs, beautifully updated kitchen and bathrooms, and all the space you could need! The kitchen features porcelain floors in a herringbone pattern, granite counter tops, a deep sink, and stainless steel appliances. The huge detached garage with walk-up attic space is a perfect set up for your favorite hobbies. The downstairs bathroom offers accessibility options such as the low curb shower with seat + both handheld & rain showerhead and grab bars. Plus, you're in the heart of Hampton - minutes from Peninsula Town Center and the Coliseum Central District, highway access and more!
